Package net.xqhs.util.logging

Class UnitLinkData

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.xqhs.util.config.Config
      • net.xqhs.util.logging.UnitLinkData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.xqhs.util.config.Configurable
    public class UnitLinkData
extends net.xqhs.util.config.Config
    A sub-configuration for linking the configured LogWrapper to another the "parent". Currently only the parentLogName is used.

    There are several effects of linking:

    • according to settings, when the "parent" log exits, the current log exits as well.
    • other effects are not currently implemented
    Author:
    Andrei Olaru
